GAMER PAT was originally authored by Kenji Saito.
The prompt-agent version was developed by Kenji Saito with GPT-5.3-Codex.

GAMER PAT is jointly developed by the Kanno and Saito laboratories at
the Graduate School of Business and Finance, Waseda University.

Here is an inevitably incomplete list of MUCH-APPRECIATED CONTRIBUTORS --
people who have designed, refined, reviewed, and operated GAMER PAT:

    Kenji Saito
    Rei Tadika
    Hiroshi Kanno

Influence note:
The GAMER PAT Main Instructions were influenced by Eddie, an editor-AI
created by Tomoyasu Hirano.
